mom-inst (0.2.16-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * Security-hardened setuid binary for non-root package installation.
  * Supports apt-get (Debian/Ubuntu) and dnf (RHEL).
  * Package deny list with glob pattern support.
  * JSON audit logging and syslog integration.

